title: The <span style="color: #D3C24D;">**[+ fvp_name +]**</span>'s Proposal
subtitle: The <span style="color: #D3C24D;">[+ fvp_name +]</span> has reconsidered their prior opposition.
view-if: (year >= 1933 and not lvp_formed and not dstp_maintained and next_election_time - time < 3) and fvp_alliance_seen and fvp_r < 1
